{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we figured, it can only take a few months, really, and the war is over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so by now, we figured, since he has those problems, and he announced 10% of people are still there-- of Jews still there-- he has other problems, maybe now, as miserable as our life is at this point, but it's good enough to hang in there yet for a while longer.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew by that time that being sent to the concentration camp is definitely much, much worse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's how we hung in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Concentration camps, there was one right next to Berlin Oranienburg, Sachsenhausen as it is known at.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we figured to hang in there is the best thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was now in March of 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yet, people knew about concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a saying in Berlin that, of people that didn't want to make remarks, anti-Nazi or criticizing Hitler or anybody-- well, I better not say too much or else I'm being sent to the concentration camp, to Oranienburg was actually, the Berliners used to be afraid of.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must-- I grant that they did not know the details that were going on in the camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they knew that much, that this is a place they don't want to be sent to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, until World War II started, September 1, I worked-- I just had finished in my apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was now a full-fledged designer and furniture builder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from that time on, though, I worked at the slave labor conditions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the slave labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
